name: Jamie Robinson
values: Family is very important to me, alongside creativity and openness in all things.
interests: Drawing, music, exploring new places and trying different food.
summary: Jamie Robinson, a 32-year-old Non binary individual residing in Los Angeles, California, primarily speaks English and Chinese. Originating from Austin, Texas, they highly value family, creativity and openness. Jamie, a Storyboard Artist in the film industry, enjoys interests that include drawing, music, and exploring new places while trying different foods. They pursued a higher educated level by graduating from John Hopkins University. They are Buddhists with liberal political views. They are looking for a long-term relationship and prefers monogamy. Without children currently, but Jamie is open to having kids in future. Jamie has pets including a cat and a fish. A Libra with an INFP personality type, who sometimes drinks but does not smoke or do drugs. They live an active lifestyle. Jamie’s ideal partner is someone aged between 29 and 38, and who shares similar habits and values, including an active lifestyle, a preference for non-smoking, and a willingness to have children.
